, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-01-09 08:31:23.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->SCORTES] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-01-09 09:06:01.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->RANGELYS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

     FROM  cma_DFactura a

     FROM  cma_DFactura a

[2020-01-09 09:36:52.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->RANGELYS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-01-09 09:54:48.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->RANGELYS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-01-09 10:27:42.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->RANGELYS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-01-09 10:29:57.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->RANGELYS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-01-09 11:01:27.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->RANGELYS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='1/9/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario

, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu

LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

select 'Sueroterapia' as Descripcion, 3 as id  
union  
select 'Laser' as Descripcion, 4 as id  
union 
select 'Intravenoso' as Descripcion, 5 as id  
union 
select 'Bloqueo' as Descripcion, 6 as id  
union 
select 'Celulas Madres' as Descripcion, 7 as id  
order by id

[2020-01-09 15:33:03.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->RANGELYS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='01/10/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac
